data.description: Welcome to 754 Apple Tree Way, a well-maintained home in the desirable Rice Ranch community of Orcutt. This beautiful single-story residence has 3 bedrooms plus a bonus room, and 2 bathrooms. The open concept floor plan features a kitchen with granite counters and a spacious island. The large great room and dining area open up, through a slider, to the covered patio and backyard. The generous primary suite is separate from the two other bedrooms which sit on either side of the bonus room. Both front and back landscape include artificial turf. Solar is on a 20-year lease prepaid by Shea Homes, with about 10 years remaining. Enjoy nearby parks, hiking and biking trails, and soccer fields, with wine tasting, golf courses, and beautiful beaches just minutes away. Easy commute to Vandenberg Space Force Base. Make this your new home and experience all that Rice Ranch and the Central Coast has to offer!
